Camelot Ghana bụ ụlọ ọrụ na-ebi akwụkwọ Ghana, na-eje ozi n'ahịa West Africa
E hiwere ụlọ ọrụ ahụ na 1963

Isi azụmahịa nke ụlọ ọrụ ahụ gụnyere ibipụta akwụkwọ, akwụkwọ kọmpụta, akwụkwọ nchekwa, na mbipụta azụmaahịa gụnyere asambodo ngwaahịa, akwụkwọ ndenye ego, akwụkwọ ndenye ego, akwụkwọ ịkwụ ụgwọ, akwụkwọ ọnụahịa na akwụkwọ ikike nke dividend.
Edepụtara ngwaahịa Camelot na Ghana Stock Exchange ma bụrụ akụkụ nke GSE All-Share Index.
